  <brief_title>Resting Postural Tremor in Multiple Sclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Spectral Analyses of Resting Postural Tremor Measured by Accelerometer and Gyroscope as a Predictive Tool of Multiple Sclerosis</official_title>
